Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:21.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:25.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I hailed us a Pegasus Carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:31.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:35.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Flying so high must've \Nbeen cold in your pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:37.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.69,0:00:41.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There, can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:56.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's my atelier and \Nthe school you'll be learning at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.98,0:02:36.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}I planted Guard Briar seeds \Naround your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:40.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,They'll grow in no time \Nand act as a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Your house was petrified \Nby an unknown spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:48.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,so it'll keep people \Nfrom getting too close to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:04.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:10.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I promised my mom I wouldn't \Nleave her by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:22.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Don't be hard on yourself. \NYou didn't know what you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Here, let's wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Let all your tears out, then look ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Because this is going to \Nbe your new home starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:59.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Um, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Hmm? Water, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:08.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah. I totally forgot! \NYou need a change of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:08.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels too round and floaty \Nto be called water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mister Qifrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:21.91,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm scared of touching \Nmagic I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.91,0:04:23.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:26.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,It's not a difficult \Nkind of magic to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Want me to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,That's a Vapor Bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:41.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,It's magic that pulls water \Nout of the moisture in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:44.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Here, hold out your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:49.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Tilt the lower tray, \Nand the water pours out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:53.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wow, that's amazing. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:54.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I love being told "Thank you."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:00.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,So thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:04.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh, um... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Thank {\i1}you{\i0} for thanking me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:12.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thank you for thanking me, \Nand thank you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:14.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Just ignore her if she's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:18.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Both,0,0,0,,She'll stop eventually if you \Njust don't respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:24.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,How mean, Richeh! I was just helping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:28.18,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The pen and ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.46,0:05:31.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Are you both witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:35.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Just apprentices. \NWe're students of Master Qifrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Wait, so you're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I totally thought you were \Na fellow student like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:45.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Are we the same age? \NWhich atelier did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:50.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I don't think I can call myself \Na student just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:54.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I mean, yesterday was \Nthe first time I ever drew a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:57.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But I'm going to live here as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:05:59.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Both,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:05.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Wait, so you're the one who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,There's a rumor going around
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:22.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,about an Outsider who used \Nforbidden magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:26.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,That they were allowed to become an \Napprentice with their memories intact...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.24,0:06:29.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.11,0:06:32.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:33.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mr. Qifrey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Looks like you all introduced yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:40.19,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Richeh and Tetia, \Nwill you go study in your rooms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,after helping with the morning chores?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.44,0:06:47.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Here are your new clothes. \NThis is what my students wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:53.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid. I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Looks like it fits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:04.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Now then, let us begin \Nthe story of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:11.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Long ago, magic wasn't something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:17.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,All you needed was a combination of \Nknown patterns and specially made ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:28.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It was a familiar tool \Nthat anyone could use.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,However, it sparked conflict \Ntime and time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,When humans are given \Nthe power to do anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,"anything" is what they will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,And so, many horrific spells were created.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:51.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The few people who still had a conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:55.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,turned away from conflict \Nand unified as witches
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.86,0:07:58.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,to take other people's memories of magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,entrusting the secret only to \Ndisciples sworn to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That was the Day of the Pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:09.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Ever since then, \Npeople have been made to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,that magic is a power only \Na chosen few can wield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,If the truth were to spread,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,the world would collapse \Ninto lawlessness once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:21.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Everyone's being careful \Nto keep the secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's why they started \Ntalking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you had to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:29.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No, I brought this on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.95,0:08:33.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Um, what's "forbidden magic"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Magic that was drawn \Nduring the age of conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,and banned when the Day of the Pact came—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:42.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,magic for hurting others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Please teach me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Teach me all about the magic \Nthat I'm not supposed to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'll be too scared to do anything \Nif I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,This is where I usually tell \Nmy students not to rush things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:02.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,but that's harder with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:06.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There are countless forbidden spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:17.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,but it's simple when you boil it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Any spell cast directly upon \Nthe human body
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:22.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,is prohibited under all circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:26.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,This includes transformation, \Nage alteration,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,teleportation without \Ndoors or conveyances,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,as well as the manipulation \Nof thoughts or emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,the harming of others, \Nor even healing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:38.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There is, however, a single exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.05,0:09:41.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Erasing memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:42.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:47.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Most spells are cast on tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:50.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Like carriages or lamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Or windows like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:22.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,A lake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.64,0:10:26.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But we were surrounded \Nby hills just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's called a Windowway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It connects two round windows \Nthat bear the same pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Can you see that building over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's the Tower of Tomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.38,0:10:41.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,To preserve knowledge, \Nall books related to magic
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:44.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,are duplicated there \Nthe moment they're written.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The picture book...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Let's go there right now! \NI won't sleep until I find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.24,0:10:51.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:10.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That was the Librarians' Trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The Tower of Tomes \Nis protected by four librarians,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,and only witches who overcome it \Nare allowed to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:21.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,So you need to study \Nif you want to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:23.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:29.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It made me happy earlier when you \Nexpressed how eager you are to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:32.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's natural to feel fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:37.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The spells that are not forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,are those that bring \Nhappiness to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:50.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,So why not learn about \Nthe gentler sort of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:55.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Yes. Of course, Master Qifrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.54,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,This'll be your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Looks like Agott's not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Who's Agott?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:13.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Your roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:21.91,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The two of you will share a workspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You'll have your own bedroom, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Go down the stairs in the back. \NDon't worry, the doors can be locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:33.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I have some things to take care of, \Nso call if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's me, Qifrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:53.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Thank you for allowing me \Nto take in Coco as my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:59.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Yes. No, nothing about the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:02.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,She's overwhelmed right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,So this is what a witch's room looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,That's my side of the desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Move so I can land.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:41.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You're Agott, right? I'm Coco—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.64,0:13:44.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You're the Outsider \Neveryone's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:48.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I heard you'll be joining as a new peer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Because of what you've done,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,she'll never return to being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:05.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I came here to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:07.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,By becoming a witch—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Our whole lives, we've been \Ndrawing Casting Seals
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,until our fingertips turned black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,We worked and worked \Nuntil we passed the tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,and were only then allowed to \Nbecome apprentices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:23.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You're an ordinary girl who knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,There's no way an Outsider such as \Nyourself can become a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:33.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I... I've drawn spells already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:35.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I won't know until I try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:37.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Then prove yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Your tests start tomorrow—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Agott! Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Food is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:45.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:57.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Me, too! We're having \NCoco's welcome party today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:58.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Lots of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:08.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Same as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.34,0:15:11.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Master, what happened \Nto the welcome party?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:15.91,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It was so last-minute. \NWe'll do it another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:17.32,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Where's Agott?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,She said she's eating in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:23.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,She should join us once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Okay, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:29.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Would you do the honors, Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:33.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.58,GJM_Main_1080p,All,0,0,0,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I know, right? We bake it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.83,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Master is a great chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:50.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:53.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the locally grown wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,We get great veggies around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.25,GJM_Main_1080p,All,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:48.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I need to take tests in order \Nto become an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:54.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But it doesn't go into detail \Nabout what you need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:56.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Need to do about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There are lots of things books \Ndon't tell you when it comes to magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:05.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You'll learn more \Nfrom doing than from reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:07.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:10.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Your Components—\Ntools used to draw magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:16.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,They look so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:21.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Ink Wand. A pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:25.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I still feel a bit scared \Ntouching this. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, I'm going to save you \Nno matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.91,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Master Qifrey, I look \Nforward to our lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:45.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Coco? \NShall we take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:53.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Okay, try explaining to me \Nwhat you learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:54.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:18:00.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Um... A spell is composed \Nof three elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The sigil is in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:06.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's surrounded by lines \Nthat are called signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:10.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The outer circle that \Ncompletes it is called the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:12.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The types of sigil—fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:14.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,water,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,light,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:18.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,and wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:21.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,They determine what kind\Nof magic it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:25.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The signs determine \Nwhat form the magic takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:27.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,as well as its size and direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.94,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Lastly, when the outer ring is completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,that locks the seal in place\Nand activates the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:39.95,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm barely keeping up \Njust memorizing everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,But you were able to explain it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.94,0:18:45.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm going to try drawing one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I like it! That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Don't throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No! Please don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's not something I can show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:15.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's sloppy, and the lines \Nare all wobbly and messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:19.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Of course it is. You're just learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,But there's something else you \Nshould pay attention to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:25.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Look right here. \NSee how your ring is not connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:28.77,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,A spell won't activate \Nunless it's a complete circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's natural to have unsteady hands when \Nyou're learning to use a new tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You're like a newborn \Nfoal just learning to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:42.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You'll get used to it and be \Nrunning around freely in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:47.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Now, connect the lines \Nand activate the spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:05.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! Very sorry! \NIt was an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Sorry! I'll dry it! I'll dry it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:14.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Calm down, Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}Has it dried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Sorry, Agott. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:16.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}Not yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:22.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,It's fine, Master. \NI'm not bothered by it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:26.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,But may I see the Casting Seal she drew?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:28.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Ah, I found the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:37.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,This sign is longer than the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:45.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,It amplified pressure in this direction\Nand caused the water to gush out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,As always, your observation \Nis on point, Agott.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:53.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I think I can leave her in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:04.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,For the next two or three days, \NI'll be out visiting the Great Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:07.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Please look after her \Nwhile I'm gone, Agott.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Absolutely, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:12.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There's a lot you can learn \Nfrom your peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:17.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Watch her closely and learn, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:21.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,M-Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:28.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Um, I'm really sorry about that. I—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You don't have to keep apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't bothered by it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Now then, Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:39.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I told you to prove yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.70,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,No more cushy little lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:46.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Your tests start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What?
